sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte App)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess

    Note over C,PA: Today's Focus: cross-view coordination on EisenKan navigation

    C->>C: User navigates to EisenKan view (click or Ctrl+3)

    C->>A: LoadNavigationContext()
    A->>PM: LoadNavigationContext()
    PM->>PA: LoadNavigationContext()
    PA-->>PM: *NavigationContext
    PM-->>A: *NavigationContext
    A-->>C: *NavigationContext

    C->>A: GetYearFocus(currentYear)
    A->>PM: GetYearFocus(currentYear)
    PM->>PA: GetYearFocus(currentYear)
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(calendar/{year}.json)
    PA-->>PM: []DayFocus
    PM-->>A: []DayFocus
    A-->>C: []DayFocus

    C->>C: resolveTodayFocus(): find entry where date == today
    C->>C: Extract themeIds and tags from today's DayFocus

    alt Today has calendar assignment
        C->>C: Set todayFocusActive = true
        C->>C: Set filterThemeIds = todayFocus.themeIds
        C->>C: Set filterTagIds = todayFocus.tags
        C->>C: EisenKan board shows only matching tasks
    else No calendar assignment for today
        C->>C: todayFocusActive remains false
        C->>C: No auto-filter applied
    end

    C->>A: SaveNavigationContext({todayFocusActive, filterThemeIds, ...})
    A->>PM: SaveNavigationContext(ctx)
    PM->>PA: SaveNavigationContext(ctx)
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(navigation_context.json) [no git commit]
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
